ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Necessary and very good if interested in trade as field. Lot of complex material to read and long problem sets to work on so not something just to drop in on out of interest I feel.
topics interesting, sometimes hard to follow lectures.
